query:
SELECT 
  id, 
  numeroCi, 
  mesServico, 
  setorSolicitante, 
  valorTotal, 
  createdAt,
  excluido
FROM despesas_v2 
WHERE YEAR(createdAt) = 2026 AND MONTH(createdAt) = 1
LIMIT 10
